China cancels a visit of a senior official to Japan amid a row over the arrest of a Chinese skipper near the disputed islands of Senkaku. (BBC)Kim Jong-un, the youngest son of North Korean leader Kim Jong-il is named as a General, the clearest sign that he will be named the successor to his father. (The Guardian)The Workers' Party of Korea conference begins in Pyongyang, North Korea. (Time) (BBC)